000000pt">o&#x301;w w</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT; font-size: 11.000000pt">&#x142;</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT; font-size: 11.000000pt">asnych Banku. </span></font>
